author: Trey Alston
title: Dua Lipa, 5SOS, Hailee Steinfeld And More Team Up To Cover An Uplifting Classic
description: Dua Lipa, 5 Seconds Of Summer, Hailee Steinfeld, and more have come together to cover Foo Fighters's 'Times Like These' for BBC One's 'The Big Night In' fundraising event.
content: BBC Radio 1 has compiled a massive lineup of artists to cover the Foo Fighters's classic 2003 tune, "Times Like These," for its new fundraising special, The Big Night In. This epic, multi-household performance features Dua Lipa, Luke Hemmings of 5 Seconds of … [+1536 chars]
